summary: Would you be able to do a Bucky x teen!reader with “Oh my god, you’re in love!” And “Wait a minutes, you’re jealous.”
question: Would you be able to do a Bucky x teen!reader with “Oh my god, you’re in love!” And “Wait a minutes, you’re jealous.”
answer:
Peter had recently brought MJ over to the tower for a catch up. You live at the tower with the Avengers, whereas Peter often visits. Today he brought MJ over but not to hang out with you, no he just brought her over to hang out with him. You’re jealous. He knows that you’re in love with MJ, or at least you think he knows. 

You sit in the lounge room with a pout, clearly showing your emotions. You put on your favourite tv show to binge. You grab some of your favourite food and settle in for the day. Nobody is really here except Steve, Bucky and Nat. You stay in your position for hours until you get up to have a quick break before going back. As you walk back into the room, you find Bucky in the kitchen.

“Hey kiddo, what’s up with you?” he says almost instantly recognising that you’re not your usual cheery self. You shrug and mutter “not much”. You sit back down and Bucky joins you. Bucky opens his mouth to say something but is cut off by fits of laughter. Not just any laughter either. It’s Peter and MJ. Your face goes into more of a grouch than it was before. Bucky connects the dots.

“Wait a minute, you’re jealous. Oh my god-” Bucky whispers to you. You panic, not wanting them to hear him so, you quickly tackle him and cover his mouth, preventing him from saying more. Peter looks at you strangely and you give him a nice big fake smile. You wait until Peter and MJ return to Peter’s room before letting Buck go. “You’re in love.” Bucky finishes his sentence.

“Could you say it any louder?”

“What’s going on in here?” Steve and Nat walk over to the two of you. You want to bang your head against a brick wall now.

“(Y/n)’s in love-” you clamp your hand over his mouth once again, and give a shy smile to Steve and Nat. Bucky tries to shout out the rest of his sentence but it comes out muffled.

“MJ, she’s in love with MJ,” Nat who’s basically your mother, sister and best friend all in one pieces it together. You sigh and unclamp your hand from Buck’s mouth. 

“No need to be ashamed or embarrassed, kiddo. It’s perfectly normal to have a crush on someone.” Steve comforts. Nat and Steve walk over to you and Buck. “What can we do to make you feel better or at least make you feel less jealous of them?”

You think real hard taking this as an opportunity to do anything with them. You remember that the local fair is on, you smile and look at the three heroes. “Well, there is something you can do…”

Angsty and like feels. Watch out! 
Mmmm I’m not sure where to start so I’m just going to dive right in. 
In Winter Soilder Sam...
body:
A tiny Sam/Rhodey rant

Angsty and like feels. Watch out!

Mmmm I’m not sure where to start so I’m just going to dive right in.

In Winter Soilder Sam alluded that he watched his wing man and best friend fall and die. There was nothing he could do. “It’s like I was just up there to watch.” Sam said to Steve after his group session at the VA. Also he stated that he had trouble finding a reason to be over seas after Riley died. Which has led me to believe that it had a profound impact on him beyond what we may have thought at the time.

Now let’s flash forward to Civil War.

Rhodey got zapped by Visions beam and fell because Sam moved. (Totally not blaming Sam BTW.) And low and behold Rhodey started to fall from hella high up. Now where does that sound familiar from? Yeah that’s right! How Riley died. Sam could have kept going but, he turned around to try and save Rhodey cause he’s a beautiful little bean, and a decent human being and that’s just what you do. Anywho. Tony was also trying to get there in time and yet they were both seconds too late. In short seeing Rhodey fall like that was all too much like how Riley fell.

I’m sure Sam thought he was going to lose Rhodey like he lost Riley. Maybe even yank up some old PTSD? Proof there dating? Yeah I think so. Marvel make them canon ASAP.
